{"tid":891282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"壹仔竟然吹捧楊生??!!!  楊受成發迹傳奇??!!!","createTime":"2018-11-06T03:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T04:51:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4520ad086ae53ee96ccecda37dce44c0debc6c7f","tid":891282,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T03:54:00.000Z","msg":"【經典〡楊受成發迹傳奇】父親受騙幾乎破產 20歲讀唔成書靠做「天文台」發圍<br />\n<br />\n楊受成的父親楊成，四零年從潮州來香港謀生，他做了兩年苦力和小販後，儲了一筆錢，便在上海街開了間錶行，名為「成安記」。而楊受成在四四年出生。<br />\n<br />\n他們家境本來很窮，後來賺到錢，就搬去尖沙咀寶勒巷住。新居有二千呎。但好景不常，幾年後，楊受成父親被朋友騙財。父親為了幫朋友，和洋行拿了幾十隻錶去抵押，一心諗着幫朋友，殊知是陷阱，騙了十幾萬，老父險些破產。幸好洋行覺得楊父為人好，讓他慢慢還款，辛辛苦苦還了四、五年才清還欠款。於是楊成又舉家搬回上海街。當時楊受成只得十三、四歲。<br />\n<br />\n楊受成讀書成績差強人意，連中學畢業證書也拿不到，至於會考成績更是不堪提了。但他對做生意則甚有興趣，二十歲中學畢業後，他用自己的積蓄在彌敦道開設了「天文台錶行」，當時舖位面積也有一千六百多呎，初嚐老闆滋味。<br />\n<br />\n他想出了「釣泥鯭」的搵客方式，每日到碼頭帶一些澳洲郵輪的遊客返店舖買錶，後來又跑到機場聯絡一些導遊和酒店司機，甚至跑到日本與當地旅遊公司聯絡以回佣作報酬搵客路。為了取得亞米茄錶分銷權，他每月數次拜訪負責代理亞米茄錶的猶太商人。他首先取得了天梭錶的分銷權，後來又取得亞米茄和勞力士的分銷權，六六年楊家在油麻地開了一間英皇鐘錶珠寶行，兩年後再在尖沙咀開一間。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：壹週刊編輯部<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20181103/634012?utm_campaign=hkad_mag_fullvideo&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=article_text_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20181103%2F634012%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_mag_fullvideo%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Darticle_text_link&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=edea878e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20181103%2F634012%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_mag_fullvideo%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Darticle_text_link&h=866c608d\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20181103/634012?utm_campaign=hkad_mag_fullvideo&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=article_text_link</a><br />\n<br />\n 楊受成認為獨沽一味做鐘錶發展有限，七三年便利用錶行賺到的錢搞地產，三年後又進軍股票，賺到盤滿鉢滿。<br />\n<br />\n當時利息只有四、五釐，他便大量購買物業，全盛時期擁有二十五個建築地盤，大嶼山也有數百萬呎的土地，預備興建一個大型度假村，市值最高有成七、八億。<br />\n<br />\n楊受成當時風生水起，除了住大屋，有兩部勞斯萊斯、平治，共六、七部車，還有兩隻遊艇，過着猶如帝皇式享受。他風流倜儻的性格，令他的名字常在娛樂版出現，與明星和港姐連在一起。亦有傳聞說他每當遇上喜歡的女仔，就會送上一隻金錶，以博取歡心。楊受成說這只是謠傳。但表示以前的確很鍾意玩。當時有錢又後生，鍾意夜晚出去食下飯，跳下舞。<br />\n<br />\n他喜歡賭馬，也因馬圈惹來牢獄之災。他的好朋友騎師告東尼在七九年涉嫌毆打《天天日報》董事韋建邦。楊受成多次接觸韋，力圖勸交，法庭指控他妨礙司法公正，判他入獄兩個月，緩刑一年。楊受成不服判決上訴，上訴遭駁回，法官認為判刑太輕，改判他入獄九個月，即時執行。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：壹週刊編輯部<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181104/634013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181104%2F634013&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4dffd8db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181104%2F634013&h=a3ceb921\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181104/634013</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有:<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181105/634026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181105%2F634026&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d8e37ec2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181105%2F634026&h=123eec03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181105/634026</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181105/634014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181105%2F634014&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4a000af7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181105%2F634014&h=ff975e58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181105/634014</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181106/634049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181106%2F634049&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=eb95befa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181106%2F634049&h=5cff6ff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181106/634049</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181106/634048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181106%2F634048&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=64cd91e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181106%2F634048&h=e4430891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181106/634048</a><br />\n<br />\n咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40a89c6251066be13851429c7d796f6878e3906","tid":891282,"uid":198188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:03:30.000Z","msg":"他的好朋友騎師告東尼在七九年涉嫌毆打《天天日報》董事韋建邦。楊受成多次接觸韋，力圖勸交，法庭指控他妨礙司法公正，判他入獄兩個月，緩刑一年。楊受成不服判決上訴，上訴遭駁回，法官認為判刑太輕，改判他入獄九個月，即時執行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5993835cda2595d94069a9e7aa02d7b670b685","tid":891282,"uid":9502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"依個富豪列傳系列<br />\n不嬲每個富豪輪住寫"},{"pid":"9d9bfc933c406dfdc00ed2e160349280dbf66d81","tid":891282,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":